paragraphs.text:
%pyspark
df =spark.read.csv(
    		path="data/titanic.csv",
    		header=True,
    		inferSchema=True, 
    		mode="DROPMALFORMED",
	    ).dropna(thresh=2,subset=('Age','Cabin'))
df.show()
